      PLDT launches Roku Powered™ TVolution streaming box     PLDT has unveiled the Roku Powered™ PLDT TVolution box to enable Filipino families to enjoy the world’s best video entertainment through an easy-to-use platform.    Read more               PLDT fibers up south Metro Manila     PLDT’s latest fiber-to-the-home rollout covers areas in Makati, Pasay, Parañaque, Muntinlupa, and Las Piñas cities, including private villages and subdivisions such as Dasmariñas Village, Better Living Subdivision, Merville, BF Homes Parañaque, and Ayala Alabang Village.   Read more             PLDT fortifies enterprise market leadership with strong Q1 growth     PLDT fortified its leadership in the Enterprise market by posting 13% growth to P8.5 billion in revenues in the first quarter compared to the same period last year, driven by strong data and ICT services uptake.   Read more              PLDT HOME posts record-breaking growth in Q1     PLDT HOME, the consumer group of PLDT, has maintained double-digit growth in its revenues in the first quarter of the year.   Read more        





     

