 Customer Service Hotline       When calling via landline   171(tollfree)   Mondays to Fridays   8:00am to 7:00pm          Saturdays & Sundays   8:00am to 5:00pm    When calling via SMART celfone   171 (toll free)           Repair Service Hotline       When calling via landline   173 (toll free)   Mondays to Fridays   8:00am to 7:00pm         Saturdays & Sundays   8:00am to 5:00pm       DSL Helpdesk       Via landline   172 (toll free)   Twenty four / Seven      

 Directory Assistance       When calling via landline     187   Mondays to Fridays   8:00am to 5:00pm     (Subscriber will be charged with P3 for every transaction)    Saturdays & Sundays   8:00am to 5:00pm     When calling via SMART celfone   187        (airtime charge applies)                 
            For Home
                Email  customercare@pldt.com.ph      Tel. No:  171          For Small and Medium Enterprises    Email  smenationinquiry@pldt.com.ph    Tel. No.  101-888          Home billing/prods and services/voice repair (landline)    Tel. No.  171/173          PLP    Tel. No.  101-328          Digitel    Tel. No.  1200          DSL tech concerns    Tel. No.  172          Fibr    Tel. No. 101–3427          Company’s Financial Status and Related Information    Email  PLDT_IR_Center@pldt.com.ph          Shareholders' Information and inquires    Email  pldtshareholderservices@pldt.com.ph           
            PLDT BUSINESS OFFICE BUSINESS HOURS
                Nationwide  Mondays to Fridays  8:00am to 5:00pm            Mall-based PLDT Business Offices are open Mondays to Sundays during mall hours.       VIA E-MAIL Send your e-mail message or inquiries at customercare@pldt.com.ph or homecare@pldt.com.ph
    

 Enterprise Customers      Tel. No.  88-ALPHA       Email  pldtalpha@pldt.com.ph       

 Other Inquiries Investors may refer to investor relations page for annual reports and other documents. Inquiries about job openings and employment should be directed to the careers section For media related content, you can browse through the News Center or email media@pldt.com.ph.    Letters to PLDT may be sent to the company's head office at:
