 The PLDT Family Would Like to Thank You... ...For the support and loyalty you’ve given us. We would not have been able to achieve continuous success if it weren’t for our millions of subscribers nationwide. We pledge to do what it takes to meet your needs and expectations and to keep developing innovative products and our quality of service. Your Feedback Means a Lot to Us To fulfill our goals for the company and our country, we need the help of our valued customers. Your feedback can make a big difference on how we work as an organization. Your questions, comments and suggestions will help us understand your digital and broadband needs and provide solutions for them. If you have brilliant ideas, please share them with us. Our team will analyze them and consider the feasible ones in our future development plans.  Are your experiencing any problem with your PLDT HOME subscription? Let us know and we’ll look into it right away. Call the PLDT hotline to get in touch with one of our customer service representatives. They will listen to your concerns and provide the right answers to your questions. 








   Give us a call: PLDT Landline:  171 (For PLDT Landline nationwide and Smart and  Talk 'N
    Text cellular phones) (02)8888171 (For NON PLDT Landlines)  FIBR:101-Fibr (3427) Home DSL: 172 Home Ultera:  *1888 (For Smart / Talk 'N Text subscribers) 02-6727277 (For PLDT NCR subscribers) 1-800-10-6727277 (Toll-free for PLDT subscribers)    Send us a tweet: Get the latest updates from PLDT HOME via Twitter. Follow and message  @PLDTHome for inquiries
and concerns. We provide advisories and different types of content, so stay in touch. Visit us at any PLDT Sales and Service Center:  Locate a PLDT Sales and Service Center near you. Drop by Jump Center (located at SM Megamall and SM Cebu) to
    experience the latest technology and gadgets.    












