PLDT Inc. Key Developments

PLDT Inc. Announces Executive Changes
Jul 19 17
PLDT Inc. announced separation from service of Madam Maria Josefina T. Gorres and Messrs. Joseph Nelson M. Ladaban and Joselito S. Limjap, Vice Presidents of the company, effective July 01, 2017. The effective date of separation of Mr. Joselito S. Limjap was moved from July 01, 2017 to October 01, 2017.


PLDT Inc. Announces Executive Separations, Effective July 1, 2017
Jun 14 17
PLDT Inc. announced the separation from service of Madam Maria Josefina T. Gorres and Messrs. Joseph Nelson M. Ladaban and Joselito S. Limjap as Vice Presidents of the company, effective July 01, 2017, due to manpower reduction program.


PLDT Inc. Declares Cash Dividend on Voting Preferred Stock for the Quarter Ending July 15, 2017, Payable on July 15, 2017
Jun 14 17
The Board of PLDT Inc. declared a cash dividend of PHP 2,437,500.00 on all of the outstanding shares of Voting Preferred Stock of the company for the quarter ending July 15, 2017, payable on July 15, 2017, to the holder of record on June 27, 2017. The cash dividend was declared out of the audited unrestricted retained earnings of the Company as at December 31, 2016, which are sufficient to cover the total amount of dividend declared.


