ShareOverviewSummaryPldt Inc. and its subsidiaries have worked on forty-two contracts worth $476,926 USD in obligations from the federal government since FY2007. In its latest active fiscal year (2016), the organization received a total of $146,254 USD in obligations.The principal agencies it has contracted with are the Department of Defense, Department of Agriculture, and Department of State.

