Overview Pldt Inc. is an internet access company in Makati, . The organization is located at Ramon Cojuangco Building. This private company was founded in 1928 (about 89 years ago).Employees Pldt Inc. employs 6,733 people. In Makati, the median number of employees at a company ranges from 18 to 1719, meaning that slightly more people work at Pldt Inc. than at the average company.
 

 










